Phase 2: Learner Input Portal (Submission Form)
React form component with all case fields
Dropdown selections for categorical fields (AI Technique, Status, Job Level, Program/Team)
Validation rules: required fields, format checks
Draft/Save/Submit workflow with status field (draft, submitted, approved)
API endpoints for draft management: POST /cases/draft, PUT /cases/{id}/submit


